一、圖書作者與內容簡介：<BR>
JP Delaney is a bestselling author of psychological thrillers. When Jane finds One Folgate Street, the unique house instantly draws her attention. Moving in, she soon learns about the death of Emma, the previous tenant of the house. As Jane tries to discover the truth, she unwittingly follows the same patterns, makes the same choices, and experiences the same terror, as the girl before.<br />
