一、圖書作者與內容簡介：<BR>
Christopher McDougall is a former war correspondent, now an editor and writer. He does his own running around his home in rural Pennsylvania. This book is about Christophers adventure to find Mexicos Tarahumara Indians, the worlds greatest distance runners, in search of an answer for one simple question: Why does my foot hurt?<br />
